Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.73,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どうして僕らは出逢ったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:49.00,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}数字なんかじゃ証明できない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:52.68,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どんな歴史も色褪せるような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.11,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}神秘のディスカバリー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:58.89,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ピタリとハマった　天声のパスワード
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.06,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}宇宙Levelのシンパシー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:09.91,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}創造紀元の胎動が聞こえているか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.49,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.27,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}極上の未来を作り出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:23.18,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}争鳴の空へと飴色のジェットで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:28.31,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}未熟な夢積み込んだらフルスロットル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:35.28,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}翔ぼう！想いのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:45.25,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:39.23,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.73,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为何我们相会于此？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:49.00,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:52.68,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.11,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:58.89,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.06,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:09.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.49,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:23.18,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:28.31,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:35.28,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:45.25,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:21.34,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち止まらず歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:24.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星を数えるより
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.78,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消せない絆が光るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:37.22,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夢は走りだした僕らを導いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:41.59,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願いを込めて描く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.81,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}守りたい気持ちはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:52.20,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち向かう勇気くれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:55.43,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まっすぐ伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:58.46,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:01.66,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けて　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:05.87,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\}忘れない胸の奥で輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.30,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君がくれた光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.31,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一緒に　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.28,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:18.31,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強く握りしめる手は暖かく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:23.76,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}このままずっと離さないよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:21.34,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一意向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:24.55,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不必计数天上星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永不消失的羁绊正在绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:37.22,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}梦想已然起步 它指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:41.59,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}倾注着梦想 描绘出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.81,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这份想要守护什么的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:52.20,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}定然会给我面对一切的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:55.43,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为我想直白地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:58.46,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唱歌吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:01.66,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}接受吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:05.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在心底发光发热 永不会被忘却的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.30,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是你给我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.31,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.28,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:18.31,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:23.76,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我永远也不会松开
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,=================INJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:59.34,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}願いはきっと叶うかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:06.08,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}熱い思いで抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:10.45,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}駆け抜けたあの日々
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:16.87,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}手と手繋いで交わした約束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:23.02,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}きっと叶う　いつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:29.40,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}ここで待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:49.06,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}一緒に過ごした秋の空の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.19,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.44,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an9\fad(200,200)\blur1\4c&H525252&}教えてくれたね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================INC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:59.34,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}愿望一定会实现的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:06.08,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}拥抱那份炽热的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:10.45,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}在奔走的那些日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:16.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}手牵手订立的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:23.02,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}一定会实现的  无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:29.40,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}我都在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:49.06,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起度过的那些秋日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.19,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.44,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}请告诉我吧
